name: SpaceBunny (alanjpan)
description:
Would you trust outer space with bunnies?

I would.

Launch the bunny commander on an expeditious journey to colonize outer space. Avoid asteroid hits, ensure your rocket launches succeed, don't fly into wormholes, and GET CARROTS! Survive five feats to obtain another highly specialized, trained, and talented BUNNY COMMANDER!!

Get as many bunny commanders to outer space as possible before you crash!
